<section class="col-6">
  <div class="row panel">
    <div class="panel-heading col-md-12">
      <div class="mt-3">已註冊的客戶</div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-12 px-5 mb-1 signCard">
      <div class="col-md-12 pt-4 px-0 mb-4">
        <div class="col-12 px-0">
          {{> alert}}
        </div>
        <h6>登入</h6>
        <div class="row pl-0">
          <p class="description pr-2 col-12">已經有帳號？在下方登入。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <form class="row needs-validation" action="/users/signin" method="POST" id="signInForm" novalidate>
        {{#if isCheckout}}
          <input type="text" name="from" value="/checkout" hidden>
        {{/if}}
        <div class="form-group col-12">
          <input type="text" name="email" class="form-control" placeholder="電子郵件地址*" autocomplete="email" required>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group col-12">
          <input type="password" name="password" class="form-control" placeholder="密碼*" autocomplete="current-password" required>
          <a href="#"><small class="form-text text-muted mt-2">忘記密碼？(尚未實裝)</small></a>
        </div>
        <br>
        <div class="col-12 text-center my-3">
          <button type="submit" class="btn sign-btn" form="signInForm">登入</button>
        </div>
      </form>
      <div class="demo-info p-3">
        <p>※ 此為 demo site，可使用以下帳號進行快速瀏覽。</p>
        <p>※ 成立訂單時，系統會發送確認郵件，如欲檢視郵件請註冊一個可使用的 Email。</p>
        <p>管理員:　root@example.com</p>
        <p>使用者:　user1@example.com</p>
        <p>密　碼:　12345678</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>